                        Opening speech UN Climate Change Conference Copenhagen
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">By minister Hanne Bjurstrøm</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[07.12.2009]</p>
                <p>Norway regrets the fact that we won’t get a comprehensive legally binding agreement in Copenhagen. However, given the circumstances, we support the approach for this meeting, which has been launched by the Danish COP presidency.</p>
                
                
