            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/md/press-centre/Press-releases/2009/teeb-report-released-on-the-economics-of.html?id=585803" title="">
                        TEEB report released on the Economics of Ecosystems and Biodiversity for National and International Policymakers
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[13.11.2009]</p>
                <p>Brussels, 13 November 2009 - Policy-makers who factor the planet’s multi-trillion dollar ecosystem services into their national and international investment strategies are likely to see far higher rates of return and stronger economic growth in the 21st century, a new report issued today says.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
